Enum Constant Detail

COMPOSITION_POLICY_CATEGORY

public static final PolicyInfo.CategoryType COMPOSITION_POLICY_CATEGORY
This category is triggered upon modification of a component. For example, a drag n' drop onto a component triggers this policy category.

FILTER_VIEW_ROLE

public static final PolicyInfo.CategoryType FILTER_VIEW_ROLE
This category is triggered upon AbstractComponent.getViewInfos(ViewType). For example, inspecting a component or opening it in its own window.

PREFERRED_VIEW

public static final PolicyInfo.CategoryType PREFERRED_VIEW
Beta. This policy can be used to select the preferred view for a component.

CAN_OBJECT_BE_CONTAINED_CATEGORY

public static final PolicyInfo.CategoryType CAN_OBJECT_BE_CONTAINED_CATEGORY
This category is used to determine whether an object can be contained in another object. This category should only rarely be used and it is likely that you should not be using this category.

SHOW_HIDE_CTRL_MANIFESTATION

public static final PolicyInfo.CategoryType SHOW_HIDE_CTRL_MANIFESTATION
Each MCTViewManifestation may be associated with a controller, which can be used when the manifestation is shown in the center pane and the inspector area. Initially, the controller is hidden and can be expanded by clicking on the twistie. This policy category controls whether the twistie is available.
